title: HandsOff! v2.1.0 [Zeus Downloads]
description:
HandsOff! v2.1.0
-------------------------------------------
Official Web Site: http://www.oneperiodic.com/products/handsoff/


Installation Instructions: 
------------------
- Open "HandsOff! v2.1.0" and Install the App.
- Open "HO21 patch" app.
- Follow the instructions listed on the Patch. If you don't see the patching instructions then click on "More Information" button.
- Enjoy.


Important Note: 
------------------
- Don't update the app. You have been warned.
- If it says that the app is damaged. Then go to the System Preferences > Security and Privacy > General > Allow apps downloaded from and Select "Anywhere".
